    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long, slender, hair brushes that come to a shaped chisel tip, used for lettering and for precise lines or bands.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指長且細窄的畫筆，筆刷末端呈尖鑿形，用於寫字或製作精確的線條或條紋。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lange, smalle haarpenselen met een beitelvormige uiteinde die worden gebruikt om te beletteren en om nauwkeurige lijnen of strepen te tekenen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
